HEADWORD: Invariance
<hw>In*va"ri*ance</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld>
<def>The property of remaining invariable under prescribed or implied
conditions.</def> <rj><au>J. J. Sylvester.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
